strings: <voice_0x010018E7><se_low>Kalderasha: Hmph, and not just to say hello to your old friend Kalderasha, I see.
<voice_0x010018E8><se_low>Kalderasha: Very well, for you, I will clear the mists for free. But you are lucky. The Great Kalderasha's usual fee is...astrological!
<voice_0x010018E9><se_low>Kalderasha: So, what hides in the mists of my crystal ball today? Let me see...

<voice_0x010018EA><se_low>Kalderasha: Yesss! YESSS! They are clearing now!
And what- WHAT is this?
